      <title>A look at Trump's first month in office. And, how to beat parental burnout</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/02/17/g-s1-49289/up-first-newsletter-trump-first-month-russia-ukraine-gaza-israel</link>
