      <title>New poll shows more support for immigration restrictions. And, this week in DOGE</title>
      <author>Suzanne Nuyen</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/02/14/g-s1-48657/up-first-newsletter-aclu-guantanamo-bay-immigration-eric-adams</link>
